{"tid":143643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將軍澳海面發現遺體證實為港台記者　港台：震驚及傷痛","createTime":"2017-03-04T18:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T18:31:47.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"62ada14a1dcb67b85b052d5b3ef8c98fcc40c7ef","tid":143643,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T18:11:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u99z2yX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu99z2yX.jpg&h=9856472d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n將軍澳工業邨對開海面，朝早發現一具遺體，證實為36歲的本台記者黃嘉熙，警方列作屍體發現案處理，由於死者頭部有傷痕，警方會調查是否有可疑，星期一會驗屍確定死因。警方在死者身上找到其錢包，內有現金。<br />\n<br />\n香港電台對此消息，感到震驚及傷痛，並對家屬致以深切的慰問。發言人說，會協助警方調查，並會盡力為家人提供一切協助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1317095-20170304.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1317095-20170304.htm&d=mdS8n1K3gC4RK9SJ0KjOq5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=99e9ffbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1317095-20170304.htm&h=459d0e5b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1317095-20170304.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7912247a9294b9d3ebd0ee58e3e8524a4bf4c732","tid":143643,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T18:12:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  RIP"},{"pid":"ed3321fb13a125b3f8d89d440068badf1cf722b3","tid":143643,"uid":42419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T18:14:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a8b5300f5d78ca5c9c0156c31c90ab4538bec3","tid":143643,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T18:15:39.000Z","msg":"殺到埋身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoj